profile.title: iOS Developer
profile.description: Hi, my name is Yevgeny Oborin (English translation is Jack) and I am professional iOS Developer from Russia, who loves making beautiful, outstanding apps. I have over 4 years of experience in software development and developed a range of applications from image-editing apps to location and social-based apps with content feeds, real-time messaging and commenting features. My #1 goal will always be to meet your needs and deadline. And if you're looking for a person who not 'just writes code', you're in right place. I developed own applications and I know every part of mobile development cycle from idea to publishing, and I can help to develop your great idea. I have experience developing own backend using BaaS solutions like Parse, Firebase. Please contact me and we will discuss how to make your app
